      "date": "2018-12-01 21:27:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-66vm5: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1fe857e5-b039-4145-b33d-b478895c550b ran 4 tests.",
